{"tid":2045111,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【港版國安法】美國制裁 杜汶澤：外交部捨得回應未呀？ 王丹：金融割喉戰中共才會痛","createTime":"2020-05-31T14:41:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-01T00:45:26.000Z","uid":25558,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4e5207b1f9688805abc7ee5424194296caf8e7fc","tid":2045111,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T14:41:28.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_743051_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_743051_0&d=jFWDEiyvEellqADaqpERGkPYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=86118638\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_743051_0&h=9f18066d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_743051_0</a><br />\n<br />\n【港版國安法】美國制裁 杜汶澤：外交部捨得回應未呀？ 王丹：金融割喉戰中共才會痛<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20200530/1536pix/1590837804_57e5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20200530%2F1536pix%2F1590837804_57e5.png&h=e5fe705e&s={SIZE}\" />    <br />\n <br />\n<br />\n針對「港版國安法」，美國總統特朗普今日（30號）凌晨宣布，香港已是「一國一制」的地方，準備制裁參與「港版國安法」立法、損害香港自治的官員等，並啟動取消香港的特殊待遇。<br />\n<br />\n中國外交部發言人華春瑩在特朗普宣布前，。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。，批評英美干涉中國事務。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。：「外交部捨得回應未呀？兩點幾喇！禮拜六唔使做呀？」<br />\n<br />\n而因八九六四，。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。，但中美關係再也回不到過去了。<br />\n<br />\n「我覺得影響深遠的是整頓美國金融市場上的中資公司這一條。。。。。。。。。。。。。他寫道。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20200530/1536pix/1590837808_eb6a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20200530%2F1536pix%2F1590837808_eb6a.jpg&h=bfe9d11c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3e1d8e34508cf7221dae520323f65a2116daadba","tid":2045111,"uid":215853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T14:42:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b782ccd4b9a7e95ebf5ac61b784834a5b19e6535","tid":2045111,"uid":47080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T15:12:24.000Z","msg":"禮拜日喇！都唔回啊<br />\n係唔係掛住去Twitter煽動美國種族暴動啊？<br />\n華嬸係正職唔係五毛啊，快撚啲回應啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c90c4cb2d6cb7b52f872e4ce78139fb67f0a383","tid":2045111,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T00:38:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4d51b8ca0b175952eb77a2b40dc3e8f27b4c997","tid":2045111,"uid":7940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T00:45:26.000Z","msg":"華大媽：I can&rsquo;t breathe <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}